SOCAL (LAX & LGB): LOW CLOUDS HAVE STRUGGLED TO DEVELOP THIS MORNING. CHANCES FOR LOW CLOUDS AND FOG FILLING IN ALONG THE COASTS CONTINUES TO FALL WITH EACH PASSING HOUR AND AT THIS RATE, MANY LOCATIONS ALONG THE COAST WILL REMAIN CLEAR THIS MORNING.
